#User Story

As a Fantasy football player.<br />
I would like to know the score a player recieved in all of my leagues.<br />
<ul>
<li>user can enter the scoring rules for each of their leagues</li>
<li>user can enter player by position and name</li>
<li>score for each league is outputted</li>
</ul>

---

As as fantasy football player.<br />
I would like to have my league rules stored for usage later.<br />
<ul>
<li>league rules are saved to a database upon creation</li>
</ul>

---

As a fantasy football player.<br />
I would like to access my leagues and no others.<br />
<ul>
<li>leagues are separated by users</li>
</ul>
